reviewText: A fun, crazy sort of movie.  Just plain out enjoyable to watch

A fun, silly movie!  A movie you can just sit back, relax and enjoy without thinking too much! From chickens to giant hamsters you won't get bored. If you like English comedies you'll like this especially with Harry, Julie Walters and Matt Lucas. How can you not love the fabulous Julie Walters! I'm hoping for a Harry Hill Movie 2.
